Maintainer: Carlos Wei <carlos.wei.hk@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/carloscn/tinyserial
Description: TinySerial - GUI serial port debug tool for Linux
 TinySerial is an open source GUI serial port debug software for Linux.
 It provides a user-friendly interface for serial communication debugging
 and testing. Based on Qt5 framework, it supports both ASCII and HEX
 data transmission modes.
 .
 Features:
  - Serial port scanning and connection
  - ASCII and HEX data format support
  - Automatic repeat sending
  - Data logging and saving
  - Cross-platform support (Linux/Windows)
